channel.title: EliteProdigyz F2P [PI]
channel.description:
[size=36pt][font=impact]Eliteprodigyz F2P[/font][/size] [size=12pt]NOTE: This is not V3[/size]
Okay lets get on with it :). Why I released. I've have this sitting on my desktop for ages it seems. I 70% fulfilled my goal on here and its gonna be my ending for this one. I also released because I never see F2p servers on here, Don't know if it is you don't like or what ha. Well Enjoy
Features: Members Objects
Unique Home (Looks like Rs Draynor!)
8+ F2p Friendly Pk teles.
Added F2p Teles of course.
Fixed some of the 2h Bugs.
Added a bit of object triggers.
Staffzone added.
Unique Member system and zone.
Prayers don't work unless your a member.
Leeches only for members/Donaters.
Made a shop with donater only Items
Has 474 Interfaces. (Loads it)
Webclient Ready!
Small File lol.
Pictures! Home map. ( I didnt do much to it like I did to v3. ) [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/30cpoy1.jpg[/img] Home Draynor (Looks like Rs.) [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/14v18og.jpg[/img] Members System [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/o5cn6v.jpg[/img] Member Items [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/35bimi8.jpg[/img]
Thats about it sooo this is a great base for a F2p server + Webclient ready!
This was a quickie had to fix compile errors before i got done. (Had like 30 lol.) Thanks to Asshole_Rule for the help on one too.
[size=18pt]Download![/size] Client: http://up.ht/iLap5s ( 597 Kb ) Source: http://up.ht/keR1d8 ( 6.8 Mb )
Credits: Legacy I think it was. And me.
Notify me if my links are down!
Note: Me no give fuck what you think. (If its bad lol) ;)
